Author:
Vol / Page:  8
Edition:
Quote:  One is so frequently exposed to the over-used, hackneyed word `Kiwi' that one is getting sick and tired of hearing it. ... From its legitimate Polynesian use for an endemic bird, it has now been stretched to include not only human beings, but lottery tickets, sportspeople, fruit, and now the dollar itself.
